org.tmotte.tmplz.load

Class Path

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tmotte.tmplz.load.Path

  • public class Path
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the address of a document to be loaded by a TextLoader. A Path contains either a java.net.URL, or a String (never both). In the latter case, the String may actually represent a URL; it is up to the TextLoaderFactory to convert it to such if it wants to.
